;arquebus, modified
;
INUMBER 696
NAME 868
WEIGHT 1000
VOLUME 10
ARTICLE SOME
PLURAL
CONTAINER IN
HIDDEN
*DESCRIPTION_START
Mounted along the two walls of the deck are a dozen heavy arquebus.
The design has been heavily modified to allow various sizes and shapes
of missiles to be launched from them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR ITEMBIT0 ! 1
    IFVAR ROUNDTIME = 0
      IFVAR ITEMVAL1 ! 1
        ECHO PLAYER You pull back the barrel, and drop in a heavy firepot.
        ECHO PLAYER [Round: 5 sec]
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
        ECHO OTHERS %n loads an arquebus.
        EQUAL ITEMBIT0 1
        AFFECT 1511
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 EXITO
        EQUAL ITEMVAL1 1
       ELSE
        ECHO PLAYER Someone is using this arquebus.
     ELSE
       STRCVT 0 ROUNDTIME
      ECHO PLAYER [Wait %0 seconds...]
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER The arquebus is already loaded.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
    IFVAR ROUNDTIME = 0
      ECHO PLAYER You jam the trigger of the arquebus forward, and the firepot shoots through the tube with an audible ZING!
      ECHO OTHERS %n launches a firepot with the arquebus.
      EQUAL ITEMVAL1 0
      EQUAL ITEMBIT0 0
      AFFECT ITEMVAL5
      IFVAR PLRSINROOM ! 0
        DAMAGEALL BURN 40 A firepot falls from above and explodes at your feet!
      ENDIF
      ELSE
        STRCVT 0 ROUNDTIME
        ECHO PLAYER [Wait %0 seconds...]
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER The arquebus is not loaded.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
