NUMBER 1503
NAME Thunderchild, Quarterdeck
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
ASTRAL
CALL 19
MONSTER_GROUP 77
*DESCRIPTION_START
You find yourself standing on the quarterdeck of the Thunderchild.
Its fire retardant decks show ample signs of use and wear, and thin
metal sheathing covers the outer hulls, as well as reinforcing the main
and foremasts. To the north, an inclined ramp leads to the forecastle,
while a short ladder to the south provides access to the poop deck. An
opening leads down into the cargo holds and quarters.
*DESCRIPTION_END
