*DESCRIPTION_START
The ship's wheel and rudder are located at the far end of this elevated
deck at the stern of Thunderchild. Coiled ropes hang from hooks set into
the ironclad wooden walls, leaving the deck clear of obstacles. A ladder
leads back down to the quarterdeck, and a door opens on a flight of
stairs leading down. A gated opening in the side leads off the ship.
