*DESCRIPTION_START
Long wooden tables and benches are bolted to the floor in orderly rows.
Warriors and mages alike, drakin and other races, put aside their armor
eat quickly before returning to battle. Someone has salvaged the sign
from the Red Dragon Tavern, and it hangs above a window where a sturdy
drakiness serves up meals.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 204 ADJ1=21 ADJ2=355

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The dented sign shows the numerous marks of where glasses and bottles
have been hurled at it. The names of the drinks and food, and their prices,
have been burned into the wood with hot irons, so as to make sure that they
are not washed away by any stray splatters of liquid.
*DESCRIPTION_END
