*DESCRIPTION_START
Iridescent scales glitter among the toppled ruins of basalt and obsidian
pillars and walls. Scattered throughout the litter are charred bones and
talons, glittering gems, grime-encrusted breastplates and armor. An air of
horror hangs heavily in the air, as if centuries have not been enough to
erase the enormity of what happened here.
