NUMBER 675
NAME Southern Island, Hidden Cave
REGION 38
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
CHANNEL 26
EXIT O 1004
ITEM 0 1508
ITEM 1 1666
;
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  ECHO PLAYER You grab hold of the edges of the chute, and hoist yourself into it.
  ECHO OTHERS %n pulls %iself into the chute.
  MOVE 3395
