*DESCRIPTION_START
The air is considerably warmer here than in the bowl, and dry. There is no sign of the havoc outside, just bare stone floors, and an eerie chittering that comes and goes. Cooler air blows down from a hole in the ceiling.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Looking closely, you realize that the hole is the outlet of a chute of some sort, leading down from an upper level.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
NUMBER 3395
NAME Hidden Chamber
REGION 38
DEEPCAVE
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 26
*DESCRIPTION_START
Light from a dozen candles glistens and sparkles off the walls, glittering with the iridescent shimmer of the scales that encrust the walls. In one corner, a comfortable bed is covered with soft furs and plump pillows. A table by the bed is laden with slightly tarnished silver goblets and plates, filled with fresh fruits and meats. A chute cut into the stone floor leads down.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1508
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  ECHO PLAYER You slide down the chute, landing in a heap at the bottom.
  ECHO OTHERS %n slides into the chute.
  MOVE 675
  POSITION LAY
  AFFECT 675
  ECHO OTHERS %n flies out of the chute and lands in a heap at your feet.
ENDIF
